        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>FinCEN Modernization Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill requires&nbsp;the Financial Crimes Enforcement Network to establish programs and perform research related to financial technology, including topics such as machine learning, data analytics, and cryptocurrency. </p>]]></text>
